    %h3 Getting started instructions:
    .code
      %ol
        %li Setup Linux distro. Ubuntu/Debian OS recommended
        %li
          Visit
          %a{:href => "https://github.com/gitlabhq/gitlabhq/blob/stable/doc/installation.md", :style => "color:#fff" } this link for setup manual
        %li Follow all steps from manual
        %li Login to GITLAB and ssh key into profile
        %li Create a first project
        %li Push some code
        %li Enjoy!
